Curse him! said Woodhull, he thinks you
are afraid to fire.
This speech had the intended effect upon
Erskine
.
Give us the signal, he said, hastily.
The signal was given, and Edward discharged
his pistol. The ball grazed Mr. Lloyd's arm, and
