You Mr. Le Vosher, or whatever your name is,
stand alongside of the table.
Monsieur believed his destiny to be fixedOh,
mon Dieu! he exclaimed;
le diable! qu'est
que c'est que a
? Vat you dovat is dat?
Tar, tar, nothing but tarstand up to the
